model

Class OutcomeSequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.OutcomeSequence

  • public class OutcomeSequence
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores an ordered sequence of outcomes using a LinkedHashSet of outcomes (Set of strings). Note: This implementation assumes that the preference variables are binary, i.e., each has a 0/1 valuation. It stores each outcome as a Set of Strings, such that the names of variables with valuation 1 are included in the set, and those with valuation 0 are not included. This methods needs to be changed if there is a need to represent sets of outcomes when preference variables are non-binary.
    Author:
    gsanthan
